title: Quarkus 1.13.7.Final released - Maintenance release
content: And here comes 1.13.7.Final, our (most probably!) last round of bugfixes for the 1.13 release. If you are not using 1.13 already, please refer to the 1.13 migration guide. Full changelog You can get the full changelog of 1.13.7.Final on GitHub. 2.0 coming soon We will soon start a new...
